<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-list>
      <v-list>
        <v-card flat>
          <v-list-item 
          prepend-icon="mdi-view-dashboard" 
          title="Home" 
          router to="/"></v-list-item>
        </v-card>
      </v-list>          
      <v-divider></v-divider>
      <v-list>
        <v-expansion-panel
        v-for="user in users"
        :key="user.title">
          
          <v-expansion-title>{{user.title}}</v-expansion-title>
        </v-expansion-panel>
      </v-list>
    <v-divider></v-divider>
      <v-list-group>
        <v-list-item 
        v-for="item in items"
        :key="item.title"
        router :to="item.route">
          <v-icon>{{item.icon}}</v-icon>
          <v-list-title>{{item.title}}</v-list-title>
        </v-list-item>
      </v-list-group>
    </v-list>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "Side-bar",
  data() {
      return {
        users:[
            {userPicture:"mdi-admin",
            title:"admin",
            route:"",
            },
        ],
        items:[
            {icon: "mdi-account-multiple-outline",
            title: "Management",
            route: "/",
            },
        ]
      }
  },
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
